window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Manning</b></p> <p>As captain of the Dallas Oilers, I was their leader on and off the ice. From the outside, it looked like I had the perfect life. I didn’t. I was married to a woman who refused to give me a divorce. All she wanted was the status title, and all I wanted was to be set free.</p> <p>It was supposed to be just another event, except it took a turn I didn’t see coming.</p> <p><b>Evelyn </b></p> <p>Attending my best friend’s bachelorette party isn’t something I was looking forward to, but it’s strange what a couple of glasses of wine will do.</p> <p>It was one night, and I thought I would never see him again - especially not coming face-to-face with him and his wife while picking up my nephew from hockey practice.</p>"; 
